                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable B</hi> 85.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction, which I got at Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the person—he was tried in the Old Court—I am sure he is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> That is right.</p>
